snippet.title: Steve RPG  - The 1.1 Update  - Trailer
snippet.description:
Steve RPG's official 1.1 update! The official name of the update is Mo' Features. The update is not out yet and does not have an official release date, however I am working hard to get it out to the public.

Play Steve RPG on GameJolt here: https://gamejolt.com/games/steve_rpg/654981



STEVE RPG IS NOT AFFILIATED WITH MICROSOFT OR MOJANG. THIS GAME WILL BE COMPLETELY FREE TO ACCOMODATE FOR THAT.
